LatexCommand eqref
reference "eq:j13"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

可以写成
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align}
 & \left\Vert \phi-\phi^{p}\right\Vert _{E}\le C\,N^{-(1/3)(k-1)}\label{eq:j14}\\
 & \left\Vert \phi-\phi^{p}\right\Vert _{E}\le C\,N^{-(2/3)\alpha}.\label{eq:j15}
\end{align}

\end_inset


